# Day 15: Dark Web Basics & Safety

## Introduction

Welcome to **Day 15** of my **30 Days of OSINT (Open Source Intelligence) Challenge**.

Today, I explored **Dark Web Basics & Safety**, one of the most misunderstood topics in cybersecurity. Many people assume the Dark Web is only used for illegal activities, but today's learning helped me understand that it also has legitimate uses, such as protecting privacy, enabling anonymous communication, and supporting journalists, researchers, and whistleblowers.

